- [ ] **Step 3: Fix `enumerateWorkers`**

In `cmd/trellis/workers.go`, replace lines 93-101:

```go
result := make(map[string][]ops.Op)
for _, logPath := range logFiles {
    workerID := ops.WorkerIDFromFilename(logPath)
    logOps, err := ops.ReadLog(logPath)
    if err != nil {
        continue
    }
    result[workerID] = append(result[workerID], logOps...)
}
```

